  "fixture_step_id_origin": {
    "notes": "Every fixture's stepId or stepIdentifier value uses the prior plan_fps numeric step numbering and was created when test/oracles/ was owned by plan_fps; the ids do not necessarily map to the current plan_vanilla_parity Phase 02 step IDs because plan_vanilla_parity renumbered Phase 02 with a different ordering (for example fixture stepId 02-007 carries stepTitle capture-demo1-playback-checkpoints but plan_vanilla_parity step 02-007 is capture-default-cfg-baseline). The current owning step file for replacing every pending fixture with live evidence is plan_vanilla_parity/steps/02-034-replace-pending-oracle-fixtures-with-live-evidence.md, and the gate that closes the oracle foundation phase is plan_vanilla_parity/steps/02-035-gate-oracle-foundation-without-deferred-status.md.",
    "current_plan_phase_02_step_count": 35,
